This is a pure python webserver implementation using pythons BaseHTTPServer.

Start by python MyLittlePythonServer.py *ip to listen on* *port number* *ipv4 or ipv6*

Sample:
for ipv4
python MyLittlePythonServer.py '127.0.0.1' 80

for ipv6 (currently NOT working)
python MyLittlePythonServer.py '::' 80 ipv6

If you dont supply a port it defaults to 8080.